			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			For the Greaves of Ro, you will need to travel to the West Commonlands.  Sometime around dusk to the dark of night, you can come across a Nightfall Giant (clever, no?).  You must slay the giant, and get the head.  Return the head to the camp of paladins, and be rewarded with the Mold for the Greaves of Ro.
